and iPadOS devices.


147
00:06:32,826 --> 00:06:36,530 line:-2
In tvOS 15, there is a new
security enhancement


148
00:06:36,563 --> 00:06:38,765 line:-2
where Apple TV
will no longer broadcast


149
00:06:38.799 --> 00:06:40.868 line:-1 align:center
Mac addresses over Bonjour.


150
00:06:40.901 --> 00:06:43.570 line:-2 align:center
Due to this change,
we can no longer prevent


151
00:06:43,604 --> 00:06:46,273 line:-2
PIN prompts
from appearing on the TV.


152
00:06:46.306 --> 00:06:49.276 line:-2 align:center
To ensure minimal impact
to your deployments,


153
00:06:49,309 --> 00:06:53,080 line:-2
we've added a new key
to the TV Remote payload.


154
00:06:53.113 --> 00:06:58.585 line:-2 align:center
Use the new TVDeviceName key
in addition to the TVDeviceID key


155
00:06:58.619 --> 00:07:02.422 line:-2 align:center
to filter Apple TV device
names in the Remote widget.


156
00:07:02,456 --> 00:07:04,892 line:-2
This will prevent any
unwanted pairing attempts


157
00:07:04.925 --> 00:07:07.461 line:-1 align:center
from managed devices.


158
00:07:07.494 --> 00:07:10.364 line:-2 align:center
A few other changes
you will want to be aware of:


159
00:07:10.397 --> 00:07:12.766 line:-2 align:center
all payload types
within a single profile


160
00:07:12.799 --> 00:07:15.169 line:-2 align:center
require unique
payload identifiers.


161
00:07:15.202 --> 00:07:17.638 line:-2 align:center
Additionally
for unsupervised devices,


162
00:07:17,671 --> 00:07:19,439 line:-2
the Take Management
prompt for apps


163
00:07:19.473 --> 00:07:21.575 line:-2 align:center
can be declined
up to three times.


164
00:07:21.608 --> 00:07:25.179 line:-2 align:center
After that, the device will
not prompt for 24 hours.


165
00:07:25.212 --> 00:07:27.748 line:-2 align:center
Also, we've updated a number
of payload keys


166
00:07:27.781 --> 00:07:29.917 line:-1 align:center
to use more inclusive language.


167
00:07:29.950 --> 00:07:32.219 line:-2 align:center
Be sure to check out
the updated Device Management


168
00:07:32.252 --> 00:07:34.555 line:-2 align:center
documentation
for more information.


